 Continuation of ISO-NEs ef forts at developing the software and related products necessary to implemen t SMD would in fact be a positive step toward ultimately developing a sin gle Northeastern market  We note however that as it continues with the d evelopment of SMD ISO-NE should be mindful of the ultimate goal of a singl e Northeastern market design  We thus urge ISO-NE to continue with develop ment of SMD in every aspect including software in a sufficiently flexible manner so that any products developed for SMD may be readily adaptable to  whatever market design is ultimately proposed for the Northeastern RTO -pg20 20 This message contains PRIVILEGED AND CONFIDENTIAL INFORMATION intended sole ly for the use of the addressees named above  Any disclosure distributi on copying or use of the information by others is strictly prohibited  If you have received this message in error please advise the sender by immed iate reply and delete the original message  Thank you20 
