 Pages 3 and 4  150 Breakpoint  I asked Kit Blair in Volume Management to review this letter and he said that it was his view and the view of two other folks in VM that the PX is vastly overstating the difficulty in calculating the 150 breakpoint  His view was that it should take hours or days but not weeks  However I do not see how we get an advantage from accelerating the calculation of refunds Finally according to reports from Credit and VM the remaining PX employees are not exactly the A-team   I suggest we should ask FERC to require the PX to document its methodology for calculating refunds so that we can review for errors  Spot audits by independent auditors might be a good idea too Steve 
