lection charge would exceed the present value of the lump sum negative CTC payment 	Obviously with respect to any settlement with Edison were extremely far apart and were therefore considering other 	options 	In the meantime the California PUC is engaged in DA and PX credit-related activities beginning next week and Edison 	will try to get the Commission to adopt their proposal 	We are working with other market participants and gearing up to vigorously oppose Edisons proposal at the PUC 	We will distribute something on Monday describing our approach and tactics at the PUC for folks to review and 	comment on 	We are scheduled to meet with Edison again next Thursday to try to knock some sense into them the probability of 	which is low If you have any questions let us know Best Jeff 
