e people on the no ICAP side than the ICAP side  Basically comes down to i economics suggests ICAP is inefficient vs ii lack of ICAP will damage competition We agreed that if ICAP is inevitable we should advocate market determined ICAPs We agreed that given that this issue is controversial and that Narshima has the largest interests  He should head up our response Scott 
